---
// About Section Component - "Nuestra Promesa"
---

<section id="sobre-nosotros" class="about section-padding">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="about-image fade-in">
        <img 
          src="/images/abogado4.png" 
          alt="Abogado FL en su oficina" 
          class="about-img" 
          loading="lazy"
          decoding="async"
          width="600"
          height="800"
          />
        <div class="experience-badge">
          <div class="badge-number">5+</div>
          <div class="badge-text">Años de<br>Experiencia</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="about-content fade-in">
        <div class="section-header">
          <span class="section-subtitle">Mi Compromiso</span>
          <h2 class="section-title">
            Comprometido con la 
            <span class="text-accent">Justicia y la Excelencia</span>
          </h2>
        </div>
        
        <p class="about-description">
          Como abogado especializado, entiendo que cada caso es único y requiere una atención personalizada.
          Me dedico a brindar representación legal de primera calidad, combinando mi experiencia y
          conocimiento con un enfoque humano y cercano a cada cliente.
        </p>
        
        <div class="about-features">
          <div class="feature-item">
            <div class="feature-icon">
              <i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-content">
              <h4>Atención Personal</h4>
              <p>Trato directo conmigo en todo momento, sin intermediarios.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="feature-item">
            <div class="feature-icon">
              <i class="fas fa-handshake"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-content">
              <h4>Confianza y Cercanía</h4>
              <p>Construyo relaciones duraderas basadas en honestidad y compromiso.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="feature-item">
            <div class="feature-icon">
              <i class="fas fa-clock"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-content">
              <h4>Disponibilidad Total</h4>
              <p>Atención personalizada y respuesta rápida cuando me necesite.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="about-actions">
          <a href="#contacto" class="btn btn-primary">Solicitar Consulta</a>
          <a href="#servicios" class="btn btn-outline">Ver Servicios</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    background-color: var(--color-light);
  }
  
  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
  }
  
  .about-image {
    position: relative;
  }
  
  .about-img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 500px;
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: 10px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-card);
  }
  
  .experience-badge {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -20px;
    right: -20px;
    background-color: var(--color-accent);
    color: var(--color-white);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 10px;
    text-align: center;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-hover);
  }
  
  .badge-number {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
  }
  
  .badge-text {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }
  
  .section-header {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  
  .section-subtitle {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }
  
  .section-title {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }
  
  .about-description {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  
  .about-features {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }
  
  .feature-item {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }
  
  .feature-icon {
    background-color: var(--color-accent);
    color: var(--color-white);
    width: 50px;
    height: 50px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  
  .feature-icon i {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
  }
  
  .feature-content h4 {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  
  .feature-content p {
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    margin: 0;
  }
  
  .about-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
    }
    
    .about-image {
      order: -1;
    }
    
    .about-img {
      height: 400px;
    }
    
    .experience-badge {
      bottom: 10px;
      right: 10px;
      padding: 1rem;
    }
    
    .badge-number {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }
    
    .section-title {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }
    
    .about-actions {
      justify-content: center;
    }
    
    .about-actions .btn {
      flex: 1;
      min-width: 200px;
    }
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .feature-item {
      flex-direction: column;
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    .about-actions {
      flex-direction: column;
    }
  }
</style>
